description: BMO US Put Write ETF has been designed to deliver an alternative income exposure by writing put options on an underlying portfolio of U.S. large cap equities. The ETF writes short-dated out-of-the-money put options by analyzing the available option premiums, while investing the portfolio in cash equivalents. The ETF may be subject to a loss if the stock prices decline significantly over the option period.
name: BMO US Put Write ETF
